  <summary>5/13/1987--Introduced.
Rural Crisis Intervention Program Act of 1987 - Amends the Rural Development Act of 1972 to provide for counseling and outreach programs to aid farmers and others who have been adversely affected by the current farm and rural economic crisis. Extends such program for an additional two years to December 23, 1990.</summary>
